column5: good one Connie  Happy B'day and many more.  Dang;;;  I thought Beans and I were the Old Farts around herel!
Happy belated birthday Connie, all the best.
Thanks OFC friends.  Your clever posts made it a fun thread for me.  Family and friends make for great birthdays.

Coach  Wishing you the happiest of birthdays - I'll bake you a cake next week!  Thank you for taking me fishing the last 15 years, its been a pleasure tagging along with you.  For those who have not met Connie, those people closest to him call him "Coach".  Thanks for coaching me to a 40+ pike, and another, and another, etc.  Happy Birthday Coach
Happy Belated Birthday Connie. I hope you enjoyed the day and have many Happy Birthdays to follow.  Mike

..........by not lighting up the 73 candles on a birthday cake for me.  If I'd had a cake and if the cake had candles.  Due to my age and some medication I'm taking, my urologist gave me a year's supply of viagra last week.   I'm going to use half of them and see if Roy wants the other two pills.  Actually being 73 is much better than that.
That's funny right there, Connie.  Happy Birthday and many more to you.
Happy Birthday Connie.  Hope you had a super day  Joey
LOL...that is too funny.  Happy belated birthday!!!
Happy birthday Connie! July was a good month, mine and my second oldest daughter`s was the 22nd.
Happy Belated Birthday Connie!  Sore arse from 73 spanks?  Gerritt.

Happy Birthday, Connie. Here I thought that smoke on the horizon was you celebrating. LOL  Just a thought to go with your viagra ....  'I've learned that it is not what you wear; it is how you take it off.'  Don

Happy Birthday!!!  Ok, belated birthday.........enjoy the viagra lol   Are you sure you want Roy to have Viagra??
Happy BD Connie...  DO NOT GIVE THOSE PILLS TO ROY!!... geeezzz its bad enough already!!
Happy Birthday Connie.  Did you hear about the break in and robbery at the viagra factory?  The police are looking for two hardened criminals.

Happy birthday connie, I got viagra and rogain for my birthday and all it did was make my hair stand up
